        <div class="sm notbold">
          
          Posted: 2010-10-21 19:58:34   | <input type="checkbox" name="quote-1287712714290915908" id="quote-1287712714290915908" class="msgQuoteCheck" onchange="multiQuote2()"/><label for="quote-1287712714290915908" onclick="multiQuote2()"> Quote</label>  | <a href="/forum.html?forum=173&amp;mid=1287712714290915908&amp;post=1&amp;replyto=1287712714290915908&amp;page=1" class="icon-replytothis" rel="nofollow">Reply to Post</a> | <a id="FOLLOW_MID_1287712714290915908" onclick="followToggle('add','1287712714290915908')" href="javascript:" class="icon-follow">Follow</a> 
